7.3 RKVY Agribusiness Incubators (R-ABIs):
RABIs would act at the implementing level for training, incubation and providing grant -in-aid support to agri start-ups. The roles and responsibilities are:
 To train and nurture agri start-ups under the program;
 To provide grant-in-aid support to selected agri start-ups;
 To assist agri-startups in scaling up their business and operations, need-based marketing, networking, technology validation support to agri start-ups;
 To assist agri startups for raising further funding;
 To build a vibrant agri-startup ecosystem by establishing a network between academia, fin

